Package com.company.backend

Class Operator

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • com.company.backend.Operator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    public class Operator
extends java.lang.Thread
    The type Operator represents the operative part of the elevator. He make the link between all object (cabin, engine, door, button) and handle all events coming from the interface. It is the operator who determines where the elevator should go.
